Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,THE SUCCESSOR OF JUSTICE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.44,0:01:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So that Underworld combat machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.69,0:01:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,dragged Master and Kilban\Ninto a different dimension?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.57,0:02:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can interfere\Nwith a duel that uses the Judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.49,0:02:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When one is defeated,\Nthey lose their head,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the Judge self-destructs, and only\Nthe winner can return to this dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What must we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you what we must do\Nto save our Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I suppose if you want to know,\Nyou have no choice but to ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't tell us, we'll defeat you\Nand force it out of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes, Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban doesn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, going over what he just said,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no viable way\Nto rescue Master from the Judge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been used to settle disputes\Nin the Underworld since ancient times!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way it can be\Ninterfered with from the outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, he's just pretending\Nto know of a way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to keep us here and deal\Nas much damage to you as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, even if he loses,\NBan will have more of an advantage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fall for the enemy's trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe in Master Aban's strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to get to the Dark King\Nas soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you're saying is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But to leave without making any attempt...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you expect us to do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:03:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mystban is an enemy\Nwe're going to have to defeat anyway.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd expect nothing less\Nfrom the Disciples of Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Aban's Feather!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does the Princess\Nhave Master's Feathers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Spellcraft and assassinations\Naren't all that I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,it's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,An Aban Strash?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the original!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aban's attack. 78 damage to Kilban.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This much damage from a single scratch?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, back there...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:06:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had really wanted to,\NI could have gravely wounded you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But instead,\NI chose to only break your mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Firstly, I couldn't afford\Nto expend all of my energy back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Secondly, I wanted your anger\Ndirected at me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This situation is exactly what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can stay here\Nfighting you for eternity...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,so long as Dai and the others\Ndefeat Ban in the meantime!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already told my intentions\Nto my successor, who will lead them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Your successor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one who can rally everyone\Nand truly make them a party of justice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is you.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I leave it to you...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Princess Leona!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Master gave me his Feathers\Nknowing this might happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to lead\Nthe Disciples of Aban to victory...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of the great Hero Aban,\Nand justice for the surface world...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Princess Leona, now command all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you must fight for the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All of you must fight for the Hero.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,From this moment forth,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,everything rests on getting Dai\Nto Ban in the best shape possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Our party must focus all of our efforts\Non this single cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark King likely has power\Nbeyond our imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The strike from the Hero's blade\Nis our greatest weapon against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When I faced the Dark Lord Hadorra,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,my friends did everything they could\Nto get me to the Dark Lord's chambers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forget about me and just go, Aban!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sir Aban, good luck to you!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just get to the Dark Lord already!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My disciples all have kind hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wonderful quality.\NBut war can be cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,At times, we must wipe aside our tears\Nand focus on achieving victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:09:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In these times, you must\Nkeep everyone moving, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you're the only one\Nwith such strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Only... me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a firm belief in justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And, as a ruler, you already have\Nwhat it takes to lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if at times\Nit means you will draw ire,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you will do what must be done\Nto lead the people down the right path.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you are quite brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want you\Nto have those Feathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If some powerful enemy\Nshould attack the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I will face that foe just as Hyunckel did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, you must lead the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to have those Feathers,\Nas proof of my faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:09:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:09:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were planning\Nto sacrifice yourself for Dai again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I merely brought you with me\Nso we could talk in private.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not looking forward to dying twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I only gave you\Nhalf of my Feathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just half the bunch, for whatever happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for worrying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, there is always\Nthe risk of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,However... I don't intend to die in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to risk my life to fight,\Nit will be "for the Hero."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Come! Let's hurry forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll teach you how to dispel\Nmagical traps on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Master didn't give me these Feathers\Nto use as weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He left them to me as beacons with which\Nto lead the disciples of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Master fights on even now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We must fight just as he does!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master is...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone is... fighting for me?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dad, Mom, and Uncle Matorif...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They all worked together like that\Nto lead the Hero to victory.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we want to call ourselves\Nthe Hero's Party,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we have to do what they did.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Otherwise, what is Master\Nfighting for right now?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can shout whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hold him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I might be a little outclassed here,\Nbut I'll do what I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stubborn enough\Nto figure something out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not be as good as Master or Mentor,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can at least do what Hyunckel did!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got my own reasons\Nfor why I've got to!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't get the wrong idea, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Comparisons to Hyunckel\Nwon't sway me to fall in love with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't imitate others\Nand just show me what you're made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mystban can reflect spells\Nthat come from straight ahead.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if I have Maam\Nbacking me up with her strength...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:13:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! You're always\Ncutting me off at the knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go!\NThe two of us will handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess and Gome, go on ahead with Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Popp and Maam are fighting\Nso I can go ahead.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In that case...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's go, Leona, Gomechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,To Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:53.49,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4}MINAKATOR{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:58.50,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}TOMAKUGUTSOSHO{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That friendship nonsense of yours...\NIt could lead to their deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We fought together all this way\Nand you still can't trust us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I was too harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Lead Dai for us, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You will stop running...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,when you hear your friends' screams.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't go any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,let's show him the combined strength\Nof the lovers to be, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm... kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop getting ahead of yourself!\NFace forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Popp and Maam\Nhave worked things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wouldn't be worried\Nif they were facing a normal enemy.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's Mystban, the last great pillar!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up! Don't think\Nyou'll be able to go after Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how do we fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You distract him. I'll finish him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you don't really\Nbelieve in my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt he can reflect a Medoroa spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But remember the Mirror of Shahal.\NIt's best to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,my Refractor Fist\Nshould be able to damage Mystban.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Refractor Fist?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inside Mystban's Shadow Raiment,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know if it was human or Darkling,\Nbut I saw a face like ours.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That means he's not\Nan evil energy life form,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but a living being with a body!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll keep him busy with my spells...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I'll tear off his Raiment\Nand hit him with my Refractor Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simple, but probably\Nthe most effective attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You ignorant fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I could easily go after Dai,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but I said the White Garden\Nwould be your grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be rude to change locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get Dai to return here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,by using your deaths as bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make us laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Underestimate us and you'll regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be one of the strongest\Nfrom the Dark Army, but you won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"...win so easily. We'll hold out."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the ones making me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe someone\Nof Ron Berku's ability could succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But you two will barely\Nserve as a distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is my prediction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill you two\Nwithout taking a single step.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:18:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That will stop Dai's progress,\Nforcing him to come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't assume everything will go...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,according to your plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Tomakugutsosho!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting tired of your parlor tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not an issue\Nif you know how it works!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}IORA!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What paltry spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hardly worth absorbing and reflecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'm sure they aren't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm using a weaker spell to keep you busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's your chance, Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Refractor...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.69,0:19:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp! Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way my Refractor Fist{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}wouldn't work on something\Nwith a physical body!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's squeezing us to death!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about us! Get to Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh no! He was letting up just enough\Nso we could call out!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that Dai would hear us!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But once Dai comes back, he'll kill us!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no point in coming to save us!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.33,0:20:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My prediction came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come!\NI'm begging you not to come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.47,0:21:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He... He managed to survive!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! It's...!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:17.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gaze at you from behind\Nas you begin to walk away{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:28.26,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}arukidasu kimi no ushirosugata wo nagameru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:36.06,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We act tough and follow our hearts{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:45.28,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}massugu de tsuyogari na sonna bokura ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we began this tale together{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:49.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hajimeta monogatari{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon something glimmers{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:56.00,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}chiheisen no mukou de kirameiteiru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:23:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've been seeking something certain{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:23:02.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tashika na mono sagashitsuzukete iruno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the distant sky, dancing in the wind{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:09.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}haruka sora ni kaze ni nori matte{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The birds sing as though\Nilluminating the future{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:15.01,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tobu tori wa naiteita mirai wo terasuyouni{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promise that connects us\NThe adventure we share{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:20.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wo tsunagu yakusoku to\Nbokura de tsumugu bouken wo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again in this world{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:26.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mata kono sekai de{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.74,0:23:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone must fight for the Hero.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.20,0:23:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leona's command\Nbrings the heroes together,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.08,0:23:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}only for them to fall into peril\Nfacing Mystban.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.08,0:23:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Larhart appears, donning the Dark Armour\NSpear, and rescues Popp and Maam.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.55,0:23:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Larhart tells of his promise to Baran{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.18,0:23:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and Dai learns of his father's intentions.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.01,0:23:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.39,0:23:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Baran's Last Will"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.97,0:24:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i}
